<br>
So there you have it.  I would like to thank everyone for taking the time to express your thoughts and feelings on this very touchy subject and also for keeping it constructive.  We have the best guild in the game and our ablity to take a subject and talk about it without getting out of hand just proves that point.  <br>
<br>
